    <h1 style="text-align: center;">PonyUPS</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center;">Banks - serve as validators of&nbsp;
      exchanges of value between participants. </p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">The Postal Service delivers exchanges of real
      goods between participants.</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">A Postal Bank provides both services to the
      general public.<br>
    </p>
